      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4764-4784",
      "markText": "一齐举箸，却如风卷残云一般，早去了一半。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33601919&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4764&rangeEnd=4784",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/321320f07200b97f321d5b6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4764&rangeEnd=4784"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33601919_37_3127-3216",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "3127-3216",
      "markText": "杜少卿道：“我如今来了。现看定了河房，到这里来居住。”季苇萧拍手道：“妙！妙！我也寻两间河房同你做邻居，把贱内也接来同老嫂作伴。这买河房的钱，就出在你！”杜少卿道：“这个自然。”",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33601919&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=3127&rangeEnd=3216",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/321320f07200b97f321d5b6?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=3127&rangeEnd=3216"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33601919_5_846-906",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "846-906",
      "markText": "不过说人生富贵功名，是身外之物；但世人一见了功名，便舍着性命去求他，及至到手之后，味同嚼蜡。自古及今，那一个是看得破的！",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33601919&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=846&rangeEnd=906",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/321320f07200b97f321d5b6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=846&rangeEnd=906"
    },
    {
