      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "6544-6587",
      "markText": "“我有一只生蛋的母鸡，你快拿集上去卖了，买几升米来煮餐粥吃，我已是饿的两眼都看不见了。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33601919&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6544&rangeEnd=6587",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/321320f07200b97f321d5b6?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6544&rangeEnd=6587"
    },
    {
