      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "11960-12019",
      "markText": "送田产的，有人送店房的，还有那些破落户，两口子来投身为仆图荫庇的。到两三个月，范进家奴仆、丫鬟都有了，钱、米是不消说了",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33601919&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11960&rangeEnd=12019",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/321320f07200b97f321d5b6?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11960&rangeEnd=12019"
    },
    {
